        <updateDate>2006-08-18T19:18:03Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Citizen Soldier Relief Act of 2006 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income military pay received by a member of a reserve component of the Armed Forces who is called or ordered to active duty for a period of more than 180 days or for an indefinite period.</p>]]></text>
